wyoming and the spring creek mine is located in montana in  cloud peak energy shipped approximately  million tons from its three mines to customers located throughout the us and around the world cloud peak energy also owns rights to substantial undeveloped coal and complimentary surface assets in the northern prb further building the company’s longterm position to serve asian export and domestic customers with approximately  total employees the company is widely recognized for its exemplary performance in its safety and environmental programs cloud peak energy is a sustainable fuel supplier for approximately three percent of the nation’s electricity back to tophome about us issues and where we stand environmental programs health and safety program sustainable development program health safety and environmental policy management colin marshall heath hill bryan pechersky gary rivenes amy clemetson bruce jones todd myers operations antelope mine cordero rojo mine spring creek mine news media press releases publications investor relations analyst coverage annual reports corporate governance email alerts events calendar frequently asked questions presentations press releases announcements business development corporate earnings operations request for information sec filings cloud peak energy inc cloud peak energy resources llc stock information webcasts careers open positions – external candidate application open positions – cloud peak employee internal application open positions – cloud peak dependent summer student  internship application recruiter services applicant rights procurement contact us site map   cloud peak energy all rights reserved · website by black hills web works microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to not delete browsing history on exit instructions for enabling cookies and configuring your bro