mpany was formed as a corporate spinoff from rio tinto energy america in   in its  annual report rio tinto stated that it held a  stake in cloud peak energy and its directly owned mines cloud peak energy also has a  stake in the decker coal company which operates the decker mine in montana  contents  operations  crow nation  notes and references  external links and further reading operationsedit the firm operates three open pit mines from thick deposits in wyoming and montana crow nationedit the firm has contracted with the crow nation to mine  million tons of coal annually on its reservation for shipment by rail to coal terminals in the pacific northwest for shipment to asia the project is called the big metal project after a legendary crow chief big metals coal is a wholly owned subsidiary of cloud peak the facilities of cloud peaks spring creek mine are located directly to the east of the reservation and will be available for the use of big metal notes and referencesedit  rio tinto rio tinto completes  per cent divestment of cloud peak energy with fully exercised over allotment media release december    cloud peak energy cloud peak energy inc announces full exercise of overallotment option by underwriters in secondary offering of common stock on behalf of selling shareholders media release december    a b rio tinto  annual report production  reserves group mines energy rio tinto website   operations cloud peak energy retrieved july     crow tribe signs coal deal supporting exports feds approve b ton coal deal with crow tribe us coal exports associated press june   retrieved july     home page website big metal coal big metal coal retrieved july    external links and further readingedit cloud peak energy official website cloud peak energy at sourcewatch retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlecloudpeakenergyoldid categories coal companies of the united statescompanies listed on the new york stock exchange navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcon